{"tid":2174563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國有大學復課一周以來呈報逾560宗新冠病毒病例","createTime":"2020-08-26T03:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T03:11:46.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"59611806cf86a25aab1043f94ddf3f451c12d09a","tid":2174563,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:05:58.000Z","msg":"美國有大學復課一周以來呈報逾560宗新冠病毒病例<br />\n2020-08-26 HKT 05:53<br />\n<br />\n&quot;美國阿拉巴馬大學自一個星期之前復課以來，呈報超過560宗病例，包括學生及教職員。校方形容挑戰不在學生，而是在於病毒，校方需要找出病毒活躍及傳播的地點，以及如何與學生、教職員及各間學院合作，減少感染情況。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545880-20200826.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545880-20200826.htm&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=09a2e8fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545880-20200826.htm&h=c000a069\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545880-20200826.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f187853fe0ce1ddc1c5156ba49bb9a309d0cc7c5","tid":2174563,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:11:46.000Z","msg":"開唔開都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}